{"tid":387862,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"老娘的草根飯堂 -日式醬燒大蔥雞肉串","createTime":"2017-09-05T03:42:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-16T17:35:06.000Z","uid":30742,"like":38,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ec6bdd33a1a32cec46f65a3ad53f6649cf520358","tid":387862,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T03:42:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/DH2CF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FDH2CF.jpg&h=8f100be6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FcDR4mLDrwA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFcDR4mLDrwA&d=5B7r%2BAZueykZiYDSZnkVXTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=9289847f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FcDR4mLDrwA</a><br />\n<br />\n老娘好鍾意閒唔使飲啤酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，又鍾意食雞（重點係雞平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n所以常常會用雞肉黎做下酒菜<br />\n好似唐揚炸雞、雞軟骨咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次做了大蔥雞肉串，<br />\n但主角唔係雞肉，而是大蔥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n醬燒過既大蔥不單唔會有辛辣味，而且甜甜的好好食！好驚喜！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結果最後我係食晒d蔥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n肉就留給某人幫手解決！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日式醬燒大蔥雞肉串： <a href=\"https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2017/09/blog-post.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.com%2F2017%2F09%2Fblog-post.html&d=5B7r%2BAZueykZiYDSZnkVXTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=ffe9b2ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2017/09/blog-post.html</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook專頁 : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foldladycanteen%2F&d=5B7r%2BAZueykZiYDSZnkVXTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=2c926f48\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2F_oldlady_%2F&d=5B7r%2BAZueykZiYDSZnkVXTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=af55953f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/</a><br />\nBlog: <a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F&d=5B7r%2BAZueykZiYDSZnkVXTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=59ea2009\" target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/</a>"},{"pid":"14136477c63b4c6509e8a5c2bf31f09015e5eb44","tid":387862,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T03:50:39.000Z","msg":"日本報紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2471e3da432610e9e1e52365edcd0668b29ece7c","tid":387862,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T03:51:14.000Z","msg":"想食老娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"308c7de48eb01cd2077ff6b0aa5cbc7046ce23f2","tid":387862,"uid":58512,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T03:52:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日本報紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 